snippet.title: Star Legions gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Star Legions, Dos PC game produced by Supernova Creations in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/star-legions/1644/
Watching the brief intro and exploring the interface in this complex sci-fi strategy game.
